            <title>[FLINK-20030] Barrier announcement causes outdated RemoteInputChannel#numBuffersOvertaken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-20030</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;numBuffersOvertaken&lt;/tt&gt; is set when the announcement is enqueued, but it can take quite a while until the checkpoint is actually started with quite a non-priority buffers being drained.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should move away from &lt;tt&gt;numBuffersOvertaken&lt;/tt&gt; and use sequence numbers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
